title: Luis Lagrutta
text: Luis María Lagrutta (born April 28, 1988 in <a href="Rafaela">Rafaela, Santa Fe</a>) is an <a href="Argentina">Argentine</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a>er who currently plays for <a href="9%20de%20Julio%20de%20Rafaela">9 de Julio de Rafaela</a> in the <a href="Torneo%20Argentino%20B">Torneo Argentino B</a>.
